                    "detailed":  "Soochipara Waterfalls, also known as Sentinel Rock Falls, is located in the Vellarimala region near Meppadi. The name \u0027Soochipara\u0027 comes from the Malayalam words \u0027Sooci\u0027 (needle) and \u0027Para\u0027 (rock), referring to the sharp needle-like rock formations around the falls. The waterfall drops down in three layers, forming a natural pool suitable for swimming. The area is part of the Western Ghats and is rich in biodiversity, offering a lush nature trail leading to the waterfall viewpoint."
